  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A lengthy rally unfolds, dominated by precise dinks in the kitchen. The primary player, Santinofuntila, demonstrates exceptional touch and consistency, waiting for the opportune moment to unleash a powerful speed-up that secures the point. This highlights a patient and strategic approach to the game.",
    "hype_announcer_charged": "OH MY GOODNESS! This is a DINK-FEST! Back and forth they go, trading marshmallows in the kitchen! But wait! Santinofuntila sees the opening! BAM! Speed-up winner! The crowd goes wild! What a point!",
    "coaching_breakdown": "Notice the patience here. The primary player is not forcing anything. They are absorbing the pace, keeping the ball low and in the kitchen. The key is the transition from defense to offense; they waited for the perfect moment to attack with pace, catching the opponent off guard. This is textbook kitchen play and strategic shot selection.",
